Als freie Jazzsängerin ist sie auch Teil der internationalen Berliner Jazzszene! Jazzmusic - love it life
Born in June, british and german citizen grew up in a happy childhood based in the wonderful happy Rhineland Germany.
As far as one can remember there always was music. Singing.  First steps in church choir, then gospel choir called „Crescendo“   First lead singing at the age of 15  in a rock girls band called ´die Männer`.
Suddenly .. and it came without a warning: Jazz entered her life! Infected by Ella Fitzgerald‘s „Airmail special“ scat  - first sight first love.


Die vierte ist fertig und wartet auf das Start Signal. Schöne Standards in bunte Farben getaucht und Originals mit Texten von der Wainwright.  #Nature girl























